<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta name="description" content="Slack Invite Automation helps users join a Slack team.">
  <meta name="og:description" content="Slack Invite Automation helps users join a Slack team.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="slack,invite,teams,workflow,users">
  <title>Slack Invite Automation: User Workflow in Slack</title>
  <%= partial 'public/partials/_head.html' %>
</head>

<body id="page-top" class="index">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
      <div class="navbar-header page-scroll">
        <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </button>
        <a class="navbar-brand page-scroll" href="#page-top">Slack Invite Automation</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
          <li class="hidden">
            <a href="#page-top"></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="page-scroll" href="#features">Features</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="page-scroll" href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="page-scroll" href="#oss">Open-Source</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="page-scroll" href="#contact">Help</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="page-scroll" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/playplayio">Follow</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.container-fluid -->
  </nav>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <div class="intro-icon">
          <img class='icon' src="img/icon.png">
        </div>
        <div class="intro-lead-in">
          <p>Wow, a landing page and form to join your Slack!</p>
          <div>Help your users join your Slack team.</div>
          <br>
          <a class="add-to-slack" href="https://slack.com/oauth/authorize?scope=bot,commands&client_id=<%= ENV['SLACK_CLIENT_ID'] %>"><img alt="Add to Slack" height="40" width="139" src="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png" srcset="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png 1x, https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack@2x.png 2x"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
          <img src="img/screenshot.png" style="max-width: 800px;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Features</h3>
          <h3 class="section-subheading">
            <div>
              <p>
                Installs in 2 clicks. No fiddling with Slack tokens or custom scripts.
              </p>
              <p>
                <a class="add-to-slack" href="https://slack.com/oauth/authorize?scope=bot,commands&client_id=<%= ENV['SLACK_CLIENT_ID'] %>"><img alt="Add to Slack" height="40" width="139" src="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png" srcset="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png 1x, https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack@2x.png 2x"></a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                Admin will be asked to authorize the bot to send invitations, once.
              </p>
              <p class="image">
                <img src="img/authorize.png" style="max-width: 400px;">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                Share the public page that lets users join Slack without an invitation.
              </p>
              <p class="image">
                <img src="img/invite.png" style="max-width: 640px;">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                Users get an email inviting them to join your team on behalf of the Slack Admin that has installed the bot.
              </p>
              <p class="image">
                <img src="img/email.png" style="max-width: 400px;">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                Optionally, turn on administrative approval from within Slack with <b>set approval on</b>.
              </p>
              <p class="image">
                <img src="img/approval.png" style="max-width: 400px;">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                When a user asks to join a team, Slack admins are DMed join requests that can be approved or ignored.
              </p>
              <p class="image">
                <img src="img/join.png" style="max-width: 400px;">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                You can change which Slack admin sends invitations with <b>set sender @username</b>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Pricing</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">
            <p>
              You can try this bot for free for 2 weeks without a credit card or personal info.
              <br>
              Subscribe for $9.99/yr thereafter. Will auto-renew.
            </p>
            <p>
              We're not trying to make money, but we need it for hosting.
            </p>
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="oss">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Open-Source</h3>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">
            <p class="image"><a href="https://github.com/vestris/slack-invite" target="_blank"><img src="img/oss.png" style="max-width: 640px;"></a></p>
            <p>The bot service is open-source under the MIT license.</p>
            <p><a href="https://github.com/vestris/slack-invite" target="_blank">Fork us on Github</a></p>
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h4 class="section-heading">Help</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">
            <p>
              <a href='https://github.com/vestris/slack-invite'>Fork me on Github</a>,
              <a href='https://github.com/vestris/slack-invite/issues/new'>open an issue</a>,
              <a href='https://twitter.com/playplayio'>tweet at @playplayio</a>,
              or <a href='mailto:dblock[at]vestris[dot]com'>e-mail dblock[at]vestris[dot]com</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="<%= SlackRubyBotServer::Service.url %>" data-text="Help users join your Slack team with Slack Invite Automation." data-via="playplayio" data-size="large" data-related="SlackAPI">Tweet</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              <a href='/privacy' target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> |
              <a href="https://www.vestris.com" target="_blank">&copy; Vestris LLC</a>
            </p>
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div id="register" class="plain" style="display: none;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <div class="row spacer"></div>
          <div id="messages" class="alert">Please wait ...</div>
          <div class="alert">
            Having trouble? <a href='https://twitter.com/playplayio' target="_blank">@playplayio</a> on Twitter
            <br><br>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="<%= SlackRubyBotServer::Service.url %>" data-text="Help users join your Slack team." data-via="playplayio" data-size="large" data-related="SlackAPI">Tweet</a>
            <br><br>
            <a href='<%= SlackRubyBotServer::Service.url %>'>Go back to invite.playplay.io.</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= partial 'public/partials/_scripts.html' %>
  <!-- Slack -->
  <script src="js/register.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
